               PERFORM S3200-UPDATE-PROC-RTN
                  THRU S3200-UPDATE-PROC-EXT
           WHEN CO-CHA-04
      *@1     산업취급이력등록(해제)결재
               PERFORM S3200-UPDATE-PROC-RTN
                  THRU S3200-UPDATE-PROC-EXT

